rows.label: qst701904_msg0001
rows.name:
Adel-sama, everyone. The unit we
dispatched to Invidia has returned.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0002
rows.name: Did everyone make it back safely?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0003
rows.name: Yes. They're all in high spirits.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0004
rows.name: That's a relief...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0005
rows.name: They returned sooner than expected.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0006
rows.name:
That's 'cause you had a great
pilot! â™ª Leave it to me.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0007
rows.name: Thank you, Maquia.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh, it's nothing. I have to
take on jobs like this now and
then to keep my skills sharp.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0009
rows.name:
Right, right. The leader
has what you're looking
for, so get it from them.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0101
rows.name: Hey... We made it back safely, somehow.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0102
rows.name:
Of course we got the Dragon
Incense. Rita even found
some top-quality stuff.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0103
rows.name:
That kid's got more potential
than I thought. She might become
a fine adventurer one day.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0104
rows.name:
It seems we were right to
have you lead, Dio-sama.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0105
rows.name: Yes. Well done, Dio, and everyone else.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0201
rows.name: We're back!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0202
rows.name:
Adventuring is so much
fun! Invidia is such a
beautiful Divine Beast...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0203
rows.name:
I kept getting sidetracked, so I
think I annoyed everyone a little...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0204
rows.name:
But I found the Dragon
Incense, so it's all~ok!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0205
rows.name: No wonder everyone looks so exhausted.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0206
rows.name: Well done, Rita, and everyone.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0301
rows.name:
The time has come for you to see
the new and improved Ryuuryuu, mo.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0302
rows.name:
We have successfully returned
with the Dragon Incense, mo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0303
rows.name:
This was only possible because
Ryuuryuu was the leader, mo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0304
rows.name:
That's a lie, mo!
Kachocho found it, mo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0305
rows.name: Yokuyoku was the one who got it, mo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0306
rows.name:
Eldest brother is not
fit to be leader, mo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0307
rows.name:
Please cease this petty squabbling
in the presence of Emperor Hugo.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0309
rows.name: ...Well done, everyone.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0401
rows.name: I'm starving. Is there anything to eat?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0402
rows.name:
No, before food, I have to hand
over this Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0403
rows.name:
It was a real pain, you know.
Those Nopon and that bard wouldn't
listen to a word I said.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0404
rows.name: I can imagine the trouble...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0405
rows.name: Well done, Augusto, and everyone.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0501
rows.name: Hey, we're back safe.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0502
rows.name:
First, let me tell you the story
of when I broke up with Juditta.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0503
rows.name: Let's save that for another time.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0504
rows.name: Oh... That's a shame.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0505
rows.name:
Right, here's the Dragon Incense.
The Dragon's Stomach was a horribly
slimy and disgusting place.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0506
rows.name: Well done, Leo, and everyone.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0601
rows.name: I'm so tired, mo...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0602
rows.name:
Everyone was so eccentric,
it was hard to get them to
work together properly, mo.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0603
rows.name:
Augusto won't work unless his
stomach's full, and Rita gets
lost right away, mo...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0604
rows.name:
But somehow, we managed to get some
top-quality Dragon Incense, mo.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0605
rows.name:
It seems your experience as
chairman came in handy.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0606
rows.name:
It seems so. Well done,
Chairman Morumo, and everyone.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0701
rows.name: Laura-sama...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0702
rows.name:
Looking at them all, it feels
like every single person we've
met so far lent us a hand...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0703
rows.name: That's what it feels like to me.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0704
rows.name: Yes, you're right...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0053
rows.name:
*A slow montage showing the
faces of the NPCs.* *(Three
or more cuts are fine.)*

rows.label: qst701904_msg0705
rows.name: It's wonderful...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0706
rows.name: I'm so moved... I could cry...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0707
rows.name: Again...?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0708
rows.name: You cry too easily.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0709
rows.name:
But this whole affair gives
me a truly strange feeling.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0710
rows.name:
The people we've helped have in
turn lent us their strength, working
together to achieve this...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0711
rows.name: ...You can feel the power of community.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0712
rows.name:
The power of community... That's
a nice way of putting it.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0713
rows.name:
I should make a note
of this in my diary.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0714
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi, you must have
had a lot to write about
recently, haven't you?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0715
rows.name: Heh... You could say that.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0716
rows.name:
But it's also been enjoyable.
Don't you think so too, Shin?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0717
rows.name: Yes... I suppose so.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0718
rows.name:
There are times I feel things
I've never felt before.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0719
rows.name: Heh... That's a good thing.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0720
rows.name: Is it...?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0070
rows.name:
*Laura is happy that Shin is experiencing
happy times. A short pause.*

rows.label: qst701904_msg0721
rows.name:
Well, let's go deliver the
Dragon Incense. I'm sure
they're all waiting.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0722
rows.name:
You're right. Our purpose is
to cure Freja's illness.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0723
rows.name: Now, let's return to the capital.
